        "content": "<p>if i'm doing a proof over natural numbers in coq, I can say</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Coq\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">induction</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">eq</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>and this will supply <code>n = 0</code> in my context. I'm struggling with a proof lacking that in lean4.</p>",
